						<div class="postbody">Disabling and reenabling rendering during vblank does, however, give an additional 85 cycles (line -1's draw time) if you're right on the edge. In the first volume of Action 53, I had to patch NES15 to disable rendering because the multicart overhead was pushing its video memory update code just over the edge.</div>

