						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">koitsu wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I briefly skimmed (did not really look at in depth) the code yesterday while I wasn't feeling very well, and I saw some spots where it looks like you're re-setting PPUScroll/$2005 to some value like $FF.  Possibly this needs to be adjusted as to not include the area of the screen where the status bar is?  Just a thought.<br /></div><br /><br />The purpose for this is that once the scanline #$D7 is reached, the IRQ begin generated will set X scrolling to #$FF (which seems to be the beginning of the second nametable when mirroring vertically) and then store #$00 to Y scrolling (but doesn't store it to the scrollY variable) because the status bar is at the bottom of the second nametable. Then, once it runs ScrollBg next time, it will reset X scrolling back to #$00 and Y scrolling to whatever value was previously written to scrollY variable. Not sure if that's the best way to do this, but that's essentially how I'm trying to do it.<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">ScrollBg:<br />&nbsp;LDY timer0<br />&nbsp;CPY #$02<br />&nbsp;BNE SkipScroll<br />&nbsp;LDY #$00<br />&nbsp;STY scrollX<br />&nbsp;STY PPUScroll<br />&nbsp;LDX scrollY<br />&nbsp;DEX<br />&nbsp;CPX #$F0<br />&nbsp;BCC SkipScrollFix<br />&nbsp;LDX #$EF<br />SkipScrollFix:<br />&nbsp;STX scrollY<br />&nbsp;STX PPUScroll<br />&nbsp;LDY #$00<br />&nbsp;STY timer0&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;; Reset timer0<br />SkipScroll:<br />&nbsp;RTS<br /><br />ScanlineIRQSet:&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;; Set up scanline interrupt<br />&nbsp;LDA #$D7<br />&nbsp;STA IRQLacth<br />&nbsp;STA IRQReload<br />&nbsp;STA IRQEnable<br />&nbsp;RTS<br /><br />IRQ:&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;; Scanline interrupt<br />&nbsp;PHA&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;; Push A, X &amp; Y to stack<br />&nbsp;TXA<br />&nbsp;PHA<br />&nbsp;TYA<br />&nbsp;PHA<br />&nbsp;LDA #$FF&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;; Split screen<br />&nbsp;STA IRQDisable<br />&nbsp;STA scrollX<br />&nbsp;STA PPUScroll<br />&nbsp;LDA #$00<br />&nbsp;STA PPUScroll<br />&nbsp;PLA&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;; Pull A, X &amp; Y from stack<br />&nbsp;TAY<br />&nbsp;PLA<br />&nbsp;TAX<br />&nbsp;PLA<br />&nbsp;RTI</div></div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />UP SIDE DOWN A B A B B A B A Hidari migi<br />L R L R STOP &amp; DASH &amp; UP &amp; TALK Ijou nashi</div>
