						<div class="postbody">It's working almost. Just a minor issue that I'd like to get fixed. I get some kind of clipping on the first scanline where the split happens (see picture).<br />Here is what I have related to the IRQ (didn't change anything in ScrollBg which I posted in my last post):<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">ScanlineIRQSet:&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;; Set up scanline interrupt<br />&nbsp;LDA #$D8<br />&nbsp;STA IRQLacth<br />&nbsp;STA IRQReload<br />&nbsp;STA IRQEnable<br />&nbsp;RTS<br /><br />IRQ:&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;; Scanline interrupt<br />&nbsp;PHA&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;; Push A, X &amp; Y to stack<br />&nbsp;TXA<br />&nbsp;PHA<br />&nbsp;TYA<br />&nbsp;PHA<br />&nbsp;LDA #%00000111&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;; Split screen<br />&nbsp;STA IRQDisable<br />&nbsp;STA PPUAddr<br />&nbsp;LDA #%01100000<br />&nbsp;STA PPUAddr<br />&nbsp;PLA&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;; Pull A, X &amp; Y from stack<br />&nbsp;TAY<br />&nbsp;PLA<br />&nbsp;TAX<br />&nbsp;PLA<br />&nbsp;RTI</div></div>

					
